.. Map information

At first I was a bit reluctant to release this as it was made for my friends of Clan stoned, but thought id show
everyone anyway, I am not normally a fan of dust maps but thought this was a bit of an exception seeming as its
made for the stoned clan. The map took me 3 days to finish

The map includes a Radar and Nav.

Also thanks to the author of fy_dust who ever it is, a small portion of the map was based around that as the stoned clan
asked me to rework that map and this is what i came up with.

Thanks for looking.
